A '''Ram-tractor''' was an object that a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] crashed into inside the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II]] during the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]] in [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]].

[[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] mentioned it to [[Cilpar]] resistance leader [[Elscol Loro]] when he was trying to convince her of his honesty that he and [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]] were there to help her. He described flying down an unfinished service corridor in the battle station, and "I lost a good friend who ran into a ram-tractor... we had to fly seat-of-the-pants...".

